  "keyFeatures": [
    "Trie-based high-performance router with wildcard and parameter support",
    "Flexible middleware system with composable pipeline",
    "Custom request context for type-safe per-request data",
    "Built-in CORS, file serving, logging, metrics, and distributed tracing middleware",
    "First-class async/await and Swift Concurrency support via SwiftNIO",
    "TLS and HTTP/2 support via swift-nio-ssl and swift-nio-http2",
    "Result-builder DSL for declarative route definitions (HummingbirdRouter)",
    "Graceful shutdown via swift-service-lifecycle integration",
    "Codable request/response encoding with JSON and URL-encoded form support",
    "Minimal dependencies — only Apple open-source Swift packages"
  ],
